<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="78" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,439,1472]" pageId="9" pageNumber="78">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,321,475,500]" pageId="9" pageNumber="78">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Small size body (
<quantity box="[539,648,476,500]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.12" pageId="9" pageNumber="78" unit="mm" value="1.12">1.12 mm</quantity>
), elongate, light brown, shiny. Pronotum sub-cylindrical with small round punctures separated by smooth spaces. Second and third elytral intervals flat. Body with very short setae.
</paragraph>
